    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>In nomine Domini Dei Salvatoris nostri Iesu Christi. Concessimus nos domna
                            <rs key="#Vir_gloriosus/vir_sublimis">gloriosissima</rs>
                        <persName ref="#people/2002" key="#Marquis/duke">Scauniperga</persName> et
                        domnus <rs key="#Vir_gloriosus/vir_sublimis">vir gloriosissimus</rs>
                        <persName ref="#people/374" key="#Marquis/duke">Liutprand</persName> summi
                            <rs key="#Marquis/duke">ducibus</rs> gentis Langubardorum, <rs
                            key="#Intercessory">per rogum</rs>
                        <persName ref="#people/3681" key="#Intercessory #Specialized_workers"
                            >Theudpaldi</persName>
                        <rs key="#Specialized_workers">cubiculario</rs> nostro, tibi <persName
                            ref="#people/3682" key="#Specialized_workers">Punnuni</persName>
                        <rs key="#Specialized_workers">scaffardu</rs> nostro <rs
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Object #Redistributive #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_individuals"
                            >muliere nomine <name ref="Fusa">Fusa</name> cum duas infantulas suas et
                            cum <rs key="#Houses">casa</rs>, <rs key="#Wine">vinias</rs>, <rs
                                key="#Landed_possessions">territuria</rs>, omnia et in omnibus de
                            quantum eius pertenuit portionem, et fuet quondam <name ref="Pertualdus"
                                >Pertualdi</name></rs>, et habitare videtur ad <placeName
                            ref="#places/3425"
                            key="#Villages/settlements #Houses #Landed_possessions #Wine #Fiscal_property #Bridges/pontoons #Slave"
                            >Pontem Piani</placeName> et fuet de <rs key="#Subactio">subactione</rs>
                        <persName key="#Gastaldus/vicegastaldus" ref="#people/3444"
                            >Ferdulfi</persName>
                        <rs key="#Gastaldus/vicegastaldus">gastaldii</rs> nostro, quatenus amodo et
                        semper habeas et possedeas tam tu qui supra Punno quam et filiis filiorum
                        tuorum, et nullus ex nostris gastaldiis aut actionarii vel quisquam homo
                        contra ea que nostra concessit potestas quandoque ire presumas et omni in
                        tempore roborata perhenni temporibus firma permanea. Quod vero preceptum
                        concessionis dictavi ego <persName ref="#people/3490"
                            key="#Other_palatine_officer">Gaydemari</persName>
                        <rs key="#Other_palatine_officer">duddus et referendarius</rs>. Actum in <rs
                            key="#Gualdi">gualdo</rs> nostro <placeName ref="#places/3481"
                            key="#Gualdi #Fiscal_property #Residential #Palatium"
                            >Miriiaccla</placeName> mense sebtembri per indictionem tertia.
                        Feliciter.</ab>
                </div>
